## Recommended Implementation Order

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["P0: Fix gear scaling<br/>(send GEAR:3 on AUTO_ON)"] --> B["P0: Atomic JSON write<br/>(YOLO side)"]
    B --> C["P1: Add detection staleness check<br/>(bridge side)"]
    C --> D["P1: Increase DETECTION_LOSS_GRACE_S<br/>(0.2 → 0.6)"]
    D --> E["P1: Rewrite pickup sequence<br/>(open → lower → extend → creep → grip → retract → raise)"]
    E --> F["P2: Tune PROPORTIONAL_GAIN<br/>(0.5 → 0.8+)"]
    F --> G["P2: Stop-turn-go steering<br/>(reduce speed while turning)"]
    G --> H["Test & tune on real hardware"]
    H --> I["P3: Calibrate TURN_LEFT/RIGHT_SIGN"]
    H --> J["P3: Add throw/dispose step"]
    H --> K["P3: Enable ultrasonics if working"]
```

