## What Needs Physical Testing

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The following cannot be fully resolved without testing on the real robot:

1. **TURN_LEFT_SIGN / TURN_RIGHT_SIGN calibration** — put object to the left; if robot turns right → flip the sign
2. **PROPORTIONAL_GAIN value** — start at 0.85, increase if turns are still sluggish, decrease if oscillating
3. **Pickup arm timing** — ARM_DOWN_S, FOREARM_FORWARD_S, GRIP_CLOSE_S depend on arm geometry; start with estimates, refine
4. **Ultrasonic sensor viability** — check if sensors return valid data; if so, re-enable
5. **PICKUP_BBOX_MIN threshold** — place object at pickup distance, read `bbox_area` from debug logs, use that value ±20%
